org.deeplearning4j.datasets.fetchers

Class TinyImageNetFetcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.deeplearning4j.datasets.fetchers.CacheableExtractableDataSetFetcher
      • org.deeplearning4j.datasets.fetchers.TinyImageNetFetcher

  • public class TinyImageNetFetcher
extends CacheableExtractableDataSetFetcher
    Tiny ImageNet is a subset of the ImageNet database. TinyImageNet is the default course challenge for CS321n at Stanford University. Tiny ImageNet has 200 classes, each consisting of 500 training images. See: http://cs231n.stanford.edu/ and https://tiny-imagenet.herokuapp.com/
